  "text": "where \u03b3 \u03be is a closed curve enclosing \u03be. In this section, we study the number of resonances with multiplicities in \u2126 ,R,\u03b8 denoted by N ,\u03b8 (R). In view of [CITATION_1] , such regions are suitable for resonance counting.",
